e__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xxs__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Button_buttonText__7e7b1d">Bezoek de website<span class="CDS_Button_iconSpan__7e7b1d"><svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="CDS_Icon_icon__96d650 CDS_Icon_inherit__96d650" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16px" height="16px" role="img"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8 2H2v12h12V8h-1v5H3V3h5V2Zm2 1h2.293L7.646 7.646l.708.708L13 3.707V6h1V2h-4v1Z"/></svg></span></span></a></div></div></div></section><div class="styles_mobile__tu1C7"><a name="write-review-button" class="CDS_Button_button__7e7b1d CDS_Button_m__7e7b1d CDS_Button_appearance-primary__7e7b1d CDS_Button_wide__7e7b1d CDS_Button_iconLeft__7e7b1d" rel="nofollow noopener" href="/evaluate/spliff.fr" data-write-review-button-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xxs__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Button_buttonText__7e7b1d"><span class="CDS_Button_iconSpan__7e7b1d"><svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="CDS_Icon_icon__96d650 CDS_Icon_inherit__96d650" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16px" height="16px" role="img"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16 2.713 13.288 0l-1.567 1.567-9.564 9.56L0 15.996l4.934-2.223 9.145-9.14L16 2.714Zm-2.274.86.86-.86-1.298-1.3-.86.86 1.298 1.3ZM1.962 14.034l1.75-.776-.974-.975-.776 1.751Zm2.62-1.32-1.3-1.3 8.438-8.433L13.02 4.28 4.58 12.714Z"/></svg></span>Een review schrijven</span></a></div></div><div class="styles_businessInfoColumnBottom__Qfl3B"><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_appearance-default__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-m__146e7a variant_container__05pif styles_accordionCard__OxNnf" data-review-incentives-banner-variant-accordion="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 CDS_Typography_weight-heavy__68c681" weight="heavy"><button aria-controls="review-incentives-banner-variant-panel" aria-expanded="false" class="variant_button__IC5Ps" id="review-incentives-banner-variant"><span class="styles_trustShieldLogo__WGwe_"><img alt="" src="https://businessunitprofile-cdn.trustpilot.net/businessunitprofile-consumersite/public/trustpilot-shield.svg" width="25" height="30" class="styles_trustShieldImg__z4P_B"/><span class="styles_animation__QNRFp"></span></span><div class="styles_titleContainer__nh3Z4"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xxs__68c681">We gebruiken technologie om de integriteit van het platform te beschermen, maar we doen geen factchecks van reviews</span></div><svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="CDS_Icon_icon__96d650 CDS_Icon_default__96d650" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16px" height="16px" role="img"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="m8.003 10.289 5.617-6.557.76.65-6.377 7.444L1.62 4.383l.76-.651 5.623 6.557Z"/></svg></button></h2><section aria-labelledby="review-incentives-banner-variant" class="variant_content__GcvGt variant_contentPadding__q_JrG" id="review-incentives-banner-variant-panel"><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681">We verifiëren geen specifieke claims omdat reviewers hun eigen mening mogen geven. We kunnen reviews echter wel als &#x27;Geverifieerd&#x27; bestempelen als we bevestiging hebben dat er een zakelijke interactie heeft plaatsgevonden. <a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-action__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_underline__0e2efd" data-testid="review-incentives-learn-more-link-1" href="https://help.trustpilot.com/s/article/Trustpilots-review-labels?language=nl" target="_blank" data-name="trustpilots-review-labels-link">Meer informatie</a></p><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_secondParagraph__Hgl7m">Om de integriteit van het platform te beschermen, wordt elke review op ons platform – al dan niet geverifieerd – gescreend door onze geautomatiseerde software. Deze software kan inhoud identificeren en verwijderen die in strijd is met onze richtlijnen, inclusief reviews die niet zijn gebaseerd op een echte ervaring. We zijn ons ervan bewust dat we weleens wat over het hoofd zien, dus je kunt altijd reviews rapporteren waarvan je denkt dat we ze hebben gemist <a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-action__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_underline__0e2efd" data-testid="review-incentives-learn-more-link-2" href="https://help.trustpilot.com/s/article/How-consumers-can-flag-reviews-that-breach-our-guidelines?language=nl" target="_blank" data-name="how-consumers-can-flag-reviews-that-breach-our-guidelines-link">Meer informatie</a></p></section></div><div class="styles_wrapper__xUH1r"><div class="styles_heading__BeAFx"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-m__68c681">Lees wat reviewers zeggen</h2><span><span role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Tooltip" data-testid="tooltip-element" data-state="closed"><svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="CDS_Icon_icon__96d650" style="fill:#6C6C85" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16px" height="16px" role="img"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8 1a7 7 0 1 0 0 14A7 7 0 0 0 8 1ZM0 8a8 8 0 1 1 16 0A8 8 0 0 1 0 8Z"/><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7.5 7h-.75V6H8.5v5.502h.75v1h-2.5v-1h.75V7ZM6.75 4a1 1 0 1 1 2 0 1 1 0 0 1-2 0Z"/></svg></span></span></div><div class="styles_relevantReviewsSection__nog13"><article data-service-review-card-paper="true" class="styles_reviewCard__meSdm"><aside class="styles_consumerInfoWrapper__6HN5O" aria-label="Informatie over Björn"><div class="styles_consumerDetailsWrapper__4eZod"><button type="button" class="styles_btnWrapper__arGPQ" aria-label="Björn" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-:R2acl37nv6:" data-state="closed"><div class="CDS_Avatar_imageWrapper__dd7fc3" style="width:44px;height:44px;min-width:44px;min-height:44px" data-testid="consumer-avatar"><img alt="" data-consumer-avatar-image="true" loading="lazy" width="44" height="44" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent" src="https://user-images.trustpilot.com/66b5e4491a2668804b29bd06/73x73.png"/></div><span class="styles_badge__oQ9m4"><svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="CDS_Icon_icon__96d650 CDS_Icon_default__96d650" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14px" height="14px" role="img"><path class="ic-verified-user" d="M1 3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v7.989a2 2 0 0 1-1.298 1.873l-5 1.875c-.453.17-.951.17-1.404 0l-5-1.875A2 2 0 0 1 1 10.989V3Z"/><path class="ic-verified-user-check" d="M11.618 6.12a.875.875 0 1 0-1.236-1.24L7.03 8.22 5.66 6.647a.875.875 0 0 0-1.32 1.15l1.768 2.03c.041.047.086.089.135.125a.875.875 0 0 0 1.364.163l4.01-3.995Z"/></svg></span></button><a data-cpl="true" href="/users/66b5e4491a2668804b29bd06" rel="nofollow" name="consumer-profile" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_wrapper__ahpyq styles_consumerDetails__POC79" data-consumer-profile-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 styles_consumerName__xKr9c" data-consumer-name-typography="true">Björn</span><div class="styles_consumerExtraDetails__NY6RP" data-consumer-reviews-count="1"><div class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681"><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2024-08-09T11:41:31.000Z" class="" data-service-review-date-time-ago="true">9 aug 2024</time></div></div></a></div></